Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪特·科內利下士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編入第三小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃瑪·懷茲中士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為第三小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安·布魯諾上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編入第六小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金·鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏特爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是那個鞏特爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你為第七小隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名至實歸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中接受過機械化部隊訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已通過大學的後備軍官教程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且你還是加利亞的英雄 鞏特爾將軍的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 帕羅特上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有實戰經驗 突然被任命為小隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你在布魯魯撤退戰鬥中表現活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為你已有實戰經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否允許使用布魯魯撤退時獲得的戰鬥車輛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥車輛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛戰車與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有極少數人能夠進行日常保養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 將伊莎拉·鞏特爾下士編入第七小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今後可能出於各種原因備受關注
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭·梅爾姬沃特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第七小隊 作為鞏特爾少尉的下級士官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助他工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複述呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 輔佐鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇茜·埃文斯上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我偏偏是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金身邊的下級士官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能明白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興沖沖報名參加義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻遇上這種怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金·鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 久違了 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧 這不是法爾迪奧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來法爾迪奧也參加了義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是第一小隊的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒去正規軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 兩位是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金是生物學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是考古學專業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專業不同 卻好像很熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要解釋的話 可能是「臭味相投」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說不定真的是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 他也是個怪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到啊 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然如此快就決定參加義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰爭那麼反感的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…全民皆兵制度下 沒人能夠例外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避兵役 辦法有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去國外避難的話 理應也不難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯魯被佔領時 我也在當地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼見人們在戰爭中死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場目睹殘垣斷壁的城市與被毀的風車 我想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡早結束這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家能重返家園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有戰鬥的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎到義勇軍來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我們就是戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隊立正
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面由第七小隊隊長發表上任講話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 維爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不用勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是維爾金·鞏特爾 今天開始與你們並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家別這麼拘謹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 大學裡的菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連實戰經驗都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本正經當起隊長來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高·波特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布麗奇特·修塔克下士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯不服維爾金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情倒也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 有件事想問大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中最重要的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經驗啊 經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 經驗確實重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是你們的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼天真爛漫的蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著戰鬥進行 會遇到各種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦與歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快與悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都只有活著才能品嚐到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了意味著一切的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論陷入何種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活著就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點希望大家銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我帶領這支小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓會盡全力保護你們的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你們也盡全力活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不論陷入何種情況」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只要活著就有希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是比唱得還好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學高材生果然不同凡響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠那麼泛泛的演講讓我們乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠衰運的 偏偏遇上那樣的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 這支小隊另有一個不容忽視的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個圍披肩的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍防線在帝國軍的攻勢下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫退至本土內地 這就是現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不會永遠被動挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正規軍與義勇軍正在進行部隊重編
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待重整旗鼓後 立即伺機反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍的第一個目標就是這裡 沃塞爾市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃塞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾所周知 沃塞爾市系交通樞紐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之沃塞爾橋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首都蘭蒂格瑞絲沿岸道路途中最關鍵所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 敵人的利劍直刺我們咽喉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座橋樑最終落入誰手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將在很大程度上左右今後戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我義勇軍完成再編製後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速出擊前往沃塞爾市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小隊加緊做好出擊準備 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始就神經緊繃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真到危急時不會洩氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就得像隊長大人這樣樂哈哈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴肅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…你這人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧 正規軍先一步出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定沃塞爾已經被一舉拿下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是沃塞爾市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來形勢發展並不順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來沒多久 戰鬥就陷入膠著狀態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說正規軍強行渡橋 被打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難為他們了 其他橋樑全部被敵人攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是唯一的渡河途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 這場戰鬥可能會曠日持久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 貿然動手只會增加犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上從我們眼前消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 非要我明說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 隊長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打開窗戶說亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還看不出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法容忍和達魯庫斯人並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來人們都說達魯庫斯人是災星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實戰經驗的毛頭小子再指手畫腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有人聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太礙眼了 整天披著達魯庫斯花紋的衣裳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實是達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也和你們一樣是人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 「達魯庫斯之災」是沒有科學依據的傳說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 按你這麼說我是在無理取鬧了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 不如打個賭怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不願服從我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想令你們服從
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼打賭就是最省事的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種場合下 難道讓我們扔硬幣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來最大的問題是 我是否有作為隊長的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等2天 2天內見分曉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你們保證 48小時內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只靠這支第七小隊 奪回那座橋樑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽瘋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自動辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的話 大家要服從我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話既已出口 不得反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 交涉成立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是燕子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍都沒完成的任務 單憑我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要在兩天以內奪回那座橋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想也不可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 難道是在為我擔心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船到橋前自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能像你那樣晴空萬里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上天氣應該不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是2天 可能會更快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晨05:00 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全看不透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 就叫維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道會起霧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧是空氣中的水蒸氣遇冷引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還有燕子飛過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕子低飛是高空空氣變冷的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接下來得忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第七小隊對東岸敵人防衛據點發動奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有霧氣掩護 靠這點人數渡橋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不渡橋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡的是 這條河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠坦克掩護？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等同於命令我們去送死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好啦 有坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你的坦克能上天？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並非上天 而是下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們駕駛這輛Edelweiss號渡河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克這東西不是在水裡游 是在地上跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定腦子不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒聽說過乘坦克過河的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以才有它的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達作戰內容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Edelweiss號立即準備渡河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步兵部隊船上待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認己方炮火後開始靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣拿下敵方據點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我們第七小隊的第一份工作來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 真打算去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 都因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 反倒幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團結這支小隊 這是必經之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 沒有伊莎拉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰行動也無法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防水處理能堅持多久 必須在實戰中才能驗證
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你陪我冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我相信哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括Edelweiss號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離對岸還有300米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論極限潛水時間剩餘2分40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了 Edelweiss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離對岸250米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高功率 引擎熄火等同於作戰失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分鐘已經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡河完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 攻擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 真給他去到對岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓敵人摸清我們的兵力數量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 哪裡冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右轉20 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北面 集中增援北面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被完全包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大勢已去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利得讓人吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照約定 你們今後必須服從隊長指示
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽隊長的倒也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我絕不接納達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習以為常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想見你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.84,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飛奔出門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:56.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}思い出は僕を　海辺に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:56.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}回憶將我 引向海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:05.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:05.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘風飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心地良さばかりを　求めて生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一味追求安逸的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:20.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ぐるぐる同じ場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:20.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}原地踏步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}そんな僕の前に　現れた笑顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出現在我面前的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太陽のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像太陽般燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想見你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飛奔出門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑い合えるように　唄い合えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想和你共同歡笑歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:53.25,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:53.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘風飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 維爾金這傢伙夠古怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜歡他這點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道他是如何想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我叫法爾迪奧·蘭扎特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學裡有緣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是他的朋友兼保姆兼監護人吧
